## How to Test
Since this is a client-side prototype, you can run it directly in your browser.

1.  **Open [index.html](file:///C:/Users/Subrata%20Das/.gemini/antigravity/brain/861e764a-99a8-4932-a16c-0fb431fca6ff/index.html)**: Open the file in Chrome, Safari, or Edge.
2.  **Mobile View**: For the best experience, open Developer Tools (F12) and toggle the **Device Toolbar** (Ctrl+Shift+M) to simulate an iPhone 14 Pro or similar device.
3.  **Interactions**:
    - Click the **+** (FAB) button to see the "Add Expense" modal slide up.
    - Type numbers on the keypad to see the amount update.
    - Click **Save Expense** to see the button animation and modal close.
    - Click the bottom navigation icons to see the active state change.

